<http://www.spektrix.com/ccoa/event/5001ABHHSRBTQRMRKVQTDCNNRTMMJHMGD> a schema:Event;
  schema:name "Name a Seat";
  schema:description """
	<h1>Name a Seat</h1><span><br/></span><h2>Create a legacy. Make a memory. Honour a loved one.</h2><span><br/></span>A unique and personal way to make a dedication.<span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Engraved seat plaques offer you the chance to become part of the fabric of this amazing and iconic theatre. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Whatever your personal reasons for naming a seat, your gift will make a real difference and will help ensure that Confederation Centre of the Arts continues to play an exciting role for future generations to enjoy. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>Your chosen words will be engraved onto a beautiful brass plaque and affixed to one of the handsome seats in the historic theatre auditorium. Plaques remain in place for a decade, commemorating the named person’s love for extraordinary performances long into the future. <span><br/></span><span><br/></span>You will receive a charitable tax receipt for your donation, as well membership to Confederation Centre of the Arts with all the associated benefits.
""";
  schema:startDate "2030-12-31T12:00:00"^^xsd:dateTime;
  schema:location <https://spektrix.com/ccoa/location/201AGBHDRLQHNHPHKKMPKLGPMDRDTDMVL>;
